540
00:38:53,241 --> 00:38:54,081
What's this?

541
00:38:54,355 --> 00:38:55,313
I've lost my mind!

542
00:38:55,714 --> 00:38:58,631
Did I really eat this whole thing?

543
00:39:00,057 --> 00:39:00,928
I did?

544
00:39:02,978 --> 00:39:04,854
