550
00:39:14,836 --> 00:39:16,919
...for what you've done for me tonight.

551
00:39:17,635 --> 00:39:18,484
Good night.

552
00:39:19,520 --> 00:39:21,073
-Goodbye.
-Bye!

553
00:39:25,478 --> 00:39:26,323
Hey!

554
00:39:30,353 --> 00:39:31,389
