586
00:41:08,128 --> 00:41:09,418
Or do you want to go dancing?

587
00:41:11,794 --> 00:41:12,875
I don't know.

588
00:41:13,515 --> 00:41:15,145
I don't feel like anything right now.

589
00:41:19,835 --> 00:41:21,418
Should we head on
over to the Han River?

590
00:41:21,794 --> 00:41:22,752
