608
00:42:38,071 --> 00:42:38,908
Hey, Hari.

609
00:42:40,684 --> 00:42:41,530
Sungjoon.

610
00:42:42,989 --> 00:42:43,837
Sungjoon.

611
00:42:47,460 --> 00:42:48,585
True love?

612
00:42:48,710 --> 00:42:49,710
What's that?

613
00:42:49,794 --> 00:42:51,211
