618
00:42:58,977 --> 00:43:02,686
I didn't know there was
a mouse for left-handers.

619
00:43:02,851 --> 00:43:04,251
Where did you get that?

620
00:43:04,335 --> 00:43:05,691
Can you get one for me?

621
00:43:05,985 --> 00:43:07,459
