Why?

640
00:44:36,690 --> 00:44:38,148
Do you have a favour to ask of me?

641
00:44:38,668 --> 00:44:40,959
I need you to help me
curb my addiction...

642
00:44:42,293 --> 00:44:43,668
...to things that don't fit me.

643
00:44:45,835 --> 00:44:47,502
Let's go and get some lunch!

644
00:44:47,710 --> 00:44:49,126
-Yes, let's.
