to eat that's also not fattening?

646
00:44:52,377 --> 00:44:54,502
I have a meeting
with the art team, so I'll pass.

647
00:44:54,710 --> 00:44:57,251
Hyejin, can you get me
a sandwich on the way back?

648
00:44:57,543 --> 00:44:58,668
