664
00:45:35,918 --> 00:45:38,286
so he probably doesn't
have anyone to eat with.

665
00:45:39,168 --> 00:45:42,543
Have we found an outdoor location
for our upcoming photo shoot?

666
00:45:42,835 --> 00:45:44,962
Yes, Miss Cha is looking into that.

667
00:45:45,293 --> 00:45:48,335
I think we'll know by early next week.

668
00:45:49,043 --> 00:45:50,085
Oh, right.

669
00:45:51,710 --> 00:45:54,668
Did you know that Mr Ji has a girlfriend?

670
00:45:55,460 --> 00:45:56,835
Really? Should we know about that?

671
00:45:57,085 --> 00:45:58,376
Wow, with his personality?

672
00:45:58,460 --> 00:45:59,835
Crazy Joon has time for a woman?

673
00:46:00,126 --> 00:46:02,918
Oh my gosh. That's unbelievable.

674
00:46:03,335 --> 00:46:05,377
I saw him with his girlfriend
during the weekend...

675
00:46:05,835 --> 00:46:07,376
...and she was beautiful.

676
00:46:07,460 --> 00:46:09,335
-She looked like a model.
-Come on.

677
00:46:09,794 --> 00:46:12,085
Being together doesn't
necessarily mean they're an item.

678
00:46:12,418 --> 00:46:16,210
Does this mean that Han Seol
and I are seeing each other?

679
00:46:16,377 --> 00:46:19,001
Why are you bringing me into this?

680
00:46:19,168 --> 00:46:21,335
Don't take it so seriously.

681
00:46:21,627 --> 00:46:22,875
I don't like it!

682
00:46:22,959 --> 00:46:25,835
The two of you look good together.
Both of you are slightly crazy.

683
00:46:26,543 --> 00:46:28,727
-What about you and me?
-No, absolutely not.

684
00:46:43,335 --> 00:46:44,293
Yes, Hyejin.

685
00:46:45,418 --> 00:46:47,668
Do you have time tonight?

686
00:46:49,293 --> 00:46:53,835
I mean, can you make some time for me?

687
00:46:55,251 --> 00:46:56,418
How are you?

688
00:46:56,918 --> 00:46:58,875
Can I have a sandwich?

689
00:47:00,959 --> 00:47:02,875
No, give me two to go.

690
00:47:02,959 --> 00:47:04,001
Sure.

691
00:47:04,875 --> 00:47:06,377
A colleague meeting?

692
00:47:07,126 --> 00:47:08,377
No, I can't go.

693
00:47:09,377 --> 00:47:11,335
I have too much work.

694
00:47:12,001 --> 00:47:13,876
Hey, is Kim Joonwoo going to be there?

695
00:47:15,335 --> 00:47:16,335
Really?

696
00:47:16,627 --> 00:47:17,794
Hey, I'll be there.

697
00:47:19,126 --> 00:47:21,502
There's a new pushover in the office.

698
00:47:21,710 --> 00:47:25,167
I was about to work over the weekend,
but I got her to do the work.

699
00:47:25,251 --> 00:47:26,627
It's okay. I'll get her to cover me.

700
00:47:26,794 --> 00:47:28,043
See you later!

701
00:47:43,630 --> 00:47:44,685
Hello.

702
00:48:19,459 --> 00:48:23,833
Hyejin, I need you to separate this...

703
00:48:23,918 --> 00:48:26,041
-...and the make-up by concept.
-Yes.

704
00:48:26,126 --> 00:48:28,629
