by the end of the day.

705
00:48:28,714 --> 00:48:29,796
-I understand.
-Thank you.

706
00:48:29,881 --> 00:48:31,006
-Sure.
-Thanks.

707
00:48:51,876 --> 00:48:54,126
I don't think I could do this myself,
so I need your help.

708
00:48:56,543 --> 00:49:01,043
