713
00:49:24,714 --> 00:49:27,255
You need to complete that
by tonight, okay?

714
00:49:27,668 --> 00:49:28,710
Keep at it!

715
00:49:28,835 --> 00:49:29,876
Goodbye.

716
00:49:32,037 --> 00:49:33,265
