717
00:49:33,543 --> 00:49:35,293
I'll be downstairs right away. Yes.

718
00:49:38,985 --> 00:49:41,262
Oh, no and I'm in a hurry!

719
00:49:41,418 --> 00:49:43,502
Miss Cha, you should get going.
I'll clean this up.

720
00:49:43,835 --> 00:49:45,835
I'm sorry, Hyejin.
I'll leave this to you, then.

721
00:49:46,627 --> 00:49:48,377
-Goodbye!
-Thanks again!

722
00:49:58,502 --> 00:50:00,637
It burns!

723
00:50:05,752 --> 00:50:08,418
Oh, are you leaving for the day?

724
00:50:13,683 --> 00:50:14,642
Look here, Support.

725
00:50:14,931 --> 00:50:16,306
