735
00:50:50,329 --> 00:50:51,417
Goodness.

736
00:50:51,502 --> 00:50:52,751
Haven't you been here long enough?

737
00:50:52,835 --> 00:50:55,627
Don't you know where things are yet?

738
00:50:56,001 --> 00:50:57,959
Is there anything you know?

739
00:50:58,293 --> 00:51:00,043
Here are the bandages, here.

740
00:51:03,337 --> 00:51:06,091
Oh, thank you.

741
00:51:18,794 --> 00:51:21,370
See, you hold it with both hands.

742
00:51:21,874 --> 00:51:23,582
Then you open it.

743
00:51:24,066 --> 00:51:25,024
