the sticky ends will stick together.

749
00:51:56,585 --> 00:51:59,293
And why are you using
your mouth to put on a bandage?

750
00:51:59,585 --> 00:52:01,835
You don't know how to do anything.

751
00:52:03,943 --> 00:52:05,611
Take care of yourself first...

752
00:52:05,695 --> 00:52:08,355
...before you clean up after other people.
Got it?

753
00:52:13,486 --> 00:52:16,236
Why is he nagging me all of a sudden?

754
00:52:16,806 --> 00:52:18,514
Why did I get him a sandwich, anyways?

755
00:52:26,830 --> 00:52:30,162
Why does it always rain
when I walk outside these days?

756
00:53:18,695 --> 00:53:20,153
Mom.

757
00:53:22,653 --> 00:53:24,695
Mom, don't leave me.

758
00:53:25,403 --> 00:53:28,528
Mom... Mom!

759
00:54:28,943 --> 00:54:30,402
My hair is all frizzy now!

760
00:54:30,486 --> 00:54:31,943
Why is there a traffic jam?

761
00:54:32,903 --> 00:54:33,986
Who is that person?

762
00:54:35,236 --> 00:54:36,736
Oh, my!

763
00:54:37,156 --> 00:54:39,485
-I think he's insane.
-He's going to get hurt.

764
00:54:39,570 --> 00:54:40,695
What's wrong with him?

765
00:55:14,862 --> 00:55:15,986
Mr Ji!

766
00:55:16,695 --> 00:55:18,236
Are you okay?

767
00:55:18,986 --> 00:55:22,820
It's dangerous out here! Come with me!

768
00:55:35,653 --> 00:55:36,570
No.

769
00:55:38,236 --> 00:55:39,319
Mom.

770
00:55:41,695 --> 00:55:43,903
Mom, Mom.

771
00:55:44,381 --> 00:55:46,005
I'm afraid of the rain.

772
00:55:46,570 --> 00:55:48,278
Mom, the rain!

773
00:56:04,319 --> 00:56:07,820
Don't look over there and look this way.

774
00:56:13,445 --> 00:56:17,653
Nothing is going to happen.

775
00:56:19,862 --> 00:56:20,944
It's okay.

776
00:56:22,069 --> 00:56:22,944
It's okay.

777
00:56:24,069 --> 00:56:25,903
It's okay, it's okay.

778
00:56:26,653 --> 00:56:28,153
Nothing is going to happen.

779
00:56:53,986 --> 00:56:55,139
It's okay.

780
00:57:01,069 --> 00:57:04,027
I'm here with you.

781
00:57:05,736 --> 00:57:08,778
I'll be your umbrella.

782
00:57:21,236 --> 00:57:22,319
Hyejin.

783
00:57:31,778 --> 00:57:33,652
"World Left-hander's Day"

784
00:57:33,736 --> 00:57:36,027
"And the day
I met my very first friend"

