00:58:07,027 --> 00:58:08,361
"She Was Pretty"

786
00:58:08,445 --> 00:58:09,735
Did you buy that underwear in America?

787
00:58:09,820 --> 00:58:10,694
Made in the USA?

788
00:58:10,778 --> 00:58:12,611
Stop talking about underwear!

789
00:58:12,862 --> 00:58:16,527
Didn't we spend
the night together, Mr Ji?

790
00:58:16,611 --> 00:58:19,403
You have something to tell me,
don't you?

791
00:58:19,736 --> 00:58:21,611
Yes, I do.

792
00:58:21,736 --> 00:58:24,944
